title: 820-3115 quarter fan spin when LCD is plugged in
message: 820-3115 had liquid damage. It powers on and posts when the LCD is unplugged, but once you plug it in it will only quarter fan spin. Ideas?

title: 820-3115 quarter fan spin when LCD is plugged in
message: Tried another LCD? Could be short in cable/LCD.

title: 820-3115 quarter fan spin when LCD is plugged in
820-3115 quarter fan spin when LCD is plugged in
message: Short on L9008 with LCD plugged in? Remove L9008 and see if it will power on this way.
